## ğŸ”§ Customization

### Adding Projects
```javascript
// In src/constants/index.js
export const projects = [
  {
    name: "Project Name",
    description: "Project description",
    image: "/path/to/image.png",
    tech: ["React", "Three.js", "TailwindCSS"],
    demo: "https://demo-link.com",
    github: "https://github.com/link"
  },
  // ...more projects
];
```

